Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.50,0:00:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,泰瑞·烏麥克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Terry Womack.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.76,0:00:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}唯唯諾諾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.59,0:00:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鮑勃·博奇\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Bob Birch.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.06,0:00:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}不問時事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.45,0:00:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沃克總統面對著一個千瘡百孔的國會\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}President Walker has surrounded himself with a broken Congress.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.83,0:00:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他甚至還提拔國會的人進白宮\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He even brought one of them into the White House.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.59,0:00:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們整垮了經濟\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Now, they've broken the economy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.53,0:00:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還與中國起了爭端\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and put us on a collision course with China.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.04,0:00:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趁來得及  快阻止他們\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Put a stop to them before it's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.35,0:00:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}停下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.82,0:00:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}廢物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.20,0:00:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在中期選舉中表明立場\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Send a message at the midterms.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.25,0:00:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓美國變得更好\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Let's start fixing the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.33,0:00:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}為美國投票
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.68,0:00:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由美國進步之友贊助播出\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Paid for by Friends of a Better America.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.55,0:00:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩千五百萬  憑空變出來的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Twenty-five million? Out of thin air?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.54,0:00:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-初步估計是這樣    -錢是哪來的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- That's our estimate.   - Where is the money coming from?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.39,0:00:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-超級政治行動委員會    -這廣告是攻擊具體事件的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Super PACs.   - These are issue-based attack ads.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.64,0:00:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,錢是誰給的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So who's giving to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.60,0:00:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得等這季財報才能確定來源\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We can't trace the money until this quarter's filings come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.12,0:00:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中期選舉栽了  下次大選也泡湯了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We get killed in the midterms, we can kiss 2016 goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.00,0:00:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,共和黨就會佔據國會多數席位和白宮\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You can deal with the republican majority and a Republican president.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.67,0:00:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們和民主黨議會競選委員會在努力還擊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We're trying to counter with D-trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.99,0:00:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,憑空變出兩千五百萬嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Make 25 million appear out of nowhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.80,0:00:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-至少能造出點聲勢    -那不夠\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- We can make a dent.   - Dents don't cut it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.41,0:01:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管款籌得多快\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, no matter how fast we ramp up fundraising,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.24,0:01:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都補不上缺口\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}we can't close the gap.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.21,0:01:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得切斷他們的資金來源\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We have to stop their money flow.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.59,0:01:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼切\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I want to know how.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.53,0:01:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到源頭  釜底抽薪\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Locate the source and then cut off the tap.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.58,0:01:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,憑空出現這麼多錢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}With this sorta influx you can be sure that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.00,0:01:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肯定有人違規了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}somebody's not playing by the rules,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.36,0:01:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但找不到源頭就沒法告狀\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but we can't whistle-blow until we find the source.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.29,0:01:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就去找  而且趕快找到\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Then find it. And you sure as hell better find it soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.96,0:01:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在構思還擊的對策\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}In the meantime, I've been working on a proposal to counter the attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.04,0:01:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,協調全國上下發出訊息\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}A coordinated national messaging effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.96,0:01:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天晚些時候發給你們\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll be sending all of you copies later today.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.69,0:01:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們要考慮一切辦法\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, we should be open to every idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.48,0:01:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了  去幹活兒吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Now, go. Get to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.72,0:01:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗蘭克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.03,0:01:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你本該代表我控制國會\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You were supposed to steer Congress on my behalf.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.82,0:01:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我心情無比焦慮\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No one is as concerned as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.89,0:01:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真應該把你留在國會\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I shoulda kept you in the house,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.18,0:01:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向雷蒙德最初說的那樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}like Raymond suggested from day one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.55,0:01:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可你分心去摻和參議院  國情諮文\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But you've been distracted by the Senate, State of the Union,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.61,0:01:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還干預外交\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}meddling with foreign diplomacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.70,0:01:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-是你要我去談判的    -我知道我做了什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- You asked me to negotiate--   - I know what I've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.81,0:01:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也知道後果\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And I know where it's gotten us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.43,0:01:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生  攻擊我們的廣告不是因為\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Sir, the attack ads are not a result of anything--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.80,0:01:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你慌慌忙忙地到處撲火  而不是防止失火\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You're scrambling from fire to fire instead of preventing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.32,0:02:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是聯邦選舉委員會  不能變魔...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm not the FEC, I can't wave a wand--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.72,0:02:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別就知道找藉口  弗蘭克  你不止這點本事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Give me more than excuses, Frank! You're better than that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.82,0:02:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒準就是這點\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Or maybe you're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.55,0:02:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要是想找個沙袋撒氣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If you need a punching bag,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.45,0:02:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我就站在這兒讓你出氣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I will stand here and take the punches,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.68,0:02:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自我上任以來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}as I have done time and time again,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.17,0:02:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一次次做你的沙袋\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}since I swore my oath.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.71,0:02:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可我更想照你的吩咐  回去工作\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But I would much rather get back to work, as you've asked me to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.04,0:02:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你太過分了  弗蘭克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You are out of line, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.42,0:02:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不出拳就放我走吧  總統先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Dismiss me or keep swinging, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.98,0:02:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你走吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You're dismissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.83,0:02:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thank you, sir.
